title: Five a Day
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A health bar that offers fresh juices, smoothies, sandwiches, salads and wraps. Uses local suppliers. Has a long list of juices and smoothies, of which most are vegan. Offers 1 vegetarian sandwich that could possibly be made vegan. All food is made-to-order. Wi-Fi.
